ing: 1 (4 ounce) jar roasted red bell peppers, drained
n: Spicy Roasted Red Pepper and Feta Hummus
des: "I have always found hummus way too bland until I tried this! Serve with chips, pita chips or cut vegetables."
ins: Place the garbanzo beans, feta cheese, drained red peppers, lemon juice, parsley, cayenne pepper, and salt in the bowl of a food processor; blend until smooth.
